FOI Resources

* The Reporters Committee for Freedom of the Press has a comprehensive website on access to public records, including state-by-state information on laws and procedures: www.rcfp.org/ogg
* The Society of Professional Journalists has a toolkit on access to public records: www.spj.org/ethics_resources/toolkits/access-to-public-records
* The National Freedom of Information Coalition has a website with links to state and federal FOI laws and resources: www.nfoic.org
* The Sunshine in Government Initiative is a project of the American Society of News Editors that provides training and resources on access to public records: www.sunshineweek.org
